**Network Topology:**
```
Host (External)
    вҶ“
valence_middleware (8080, 8443, 9090) вҶҗ EXPOSED
    вҶ“ (internal network)
Weaviate (8080) вҶҗ SHIELDED
PostgreSQL (5432) вҶҗ SHIELDED
Redis (6379) вҶҗ SHIELDED
Ollama (11434) вҶҗ SHIELDED
```

**Deployment Command:**
```bash
docker-compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.middleware.yml up -d
```

**Result:** Core services are completely shielded from the host, accessible ONLY through the middleware proxy.

