    в””в”Җ Overhead:       128 MB (25%)
  MBU Efficiency:      75.0% вң“
  Inference:           256 tokens @ 4500ms
```

**Interpretation:**
- **MBU > 75%:** Excellent efficiency
- **MBU 70-75%:** Good efficiency
- **MBU < 70%:** Possible resource waste

